n-id="request-WEB:a68d0f87-407f-405f-879a-376e996c38bd-16" data-turn-id-container="request-WEB:a68d0f87-407f-405f-879a-376e996c38bd-16" data-testid="conversation-turn-32" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="302f7b34-5943-4b0e-ab59-f91368ba6155" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="82">Now that all your pages are ready, follow these steps to complete your assignment.</p>
<h2 data-start="84" data-end="117" data-section-id="5b3tic">1. Arrange your project folder</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="119" data-end="755"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2df4e570.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0" style=""><code><span>ArtGallery/
│── login.html
│── signup.html
│── gallery.html
│── artdisplay.html
│── monalisa.html
│── starrynight.html
│── scream.html
│── girlwithpearl.html
│── persistence.html
│
└── images/
    ├── monalisa.jpg
    ├── starrynight.jpg
    ├── scream.jpg
    ├── girlwithpearl.jpg
    ├── persistence.jpg
    ├── lastsupper.jpg
    ├── ladyermine.jpg
    ├── birthvenus.jpg
    ├── sunflowers.jpg
    ├── irises.jpg
    ├── wheatfield.jpg
    ├── anxiety.jpg
    ├── madonna.jpg
    ├── ashes.jpg
    ├── milkmaid.jpg
    ├── lacemaker.jpg
    ├── musiclesson.jpg
    ├── elephants.jpg
    ├── swans.jpg
    └── temptation.jpg</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="757" data-end="760">
<h2 data-start="762" data-end="785" data-section-id="vv4sh1">2. Test your website</h2>
<p data-start="787" data-end="832">Open <strong data-start="792" data-end="808">gallery.html</strong> or <strong data-start="812" data-end="831">artdisplay.html</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="834" data-end="845">Check that:</p>
<ul data-start="846" data-end="1000">
<li data-start="846" data-end="873" data-section-id="1ro49ta">
<p data-start="848" data-end="873">✅ All images are visible.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="874" data-end="927" data-section-id="bhdadx">
<p data-start="876" data-end="927">✅ Clicking <strong data-start="887" data-end="895">View</strong> opens the correct artwork page.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="928" data-end="969" data-section-id="ccwgw6">
<p data-start="930" data-end="969">✅ The <strong data-start="936" data-end="955">Back to Gallery</strong> button works.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="970" data-end="1000" data-section-id="orxpw4">
<p data-start="972" data-end="1000">✅ No image icons are broken.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1002" data-end="1005">
<h2 data-start="1007" data-end="1028" data-section-id="7l8k53">3. Zip the project</h2>
<p data-start="1030" data-end="1068">Right-click the <strong data-start="1046" data-end="1060">ArtGallery</strong> folder.</p>
<p data-start="1070" data-end="1077">Choose:</p>
<p data-start="1079" data-end="1119"><strong data-start="1079" data-end="1119">Send to → Compressed (zipped) folder</strong></p>
<p data-start="1121" data-end="1134">This creates:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1136" data-end="1158"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2df4e570.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>ArtGallery.zip</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1160" data-end="1163">
<h2 data-start="1165" data-end="1187" data-section-id="1n9uzs2">4. Upload to GitHub</h2>
<ol data-start="1189" data-end="1274">
<li data-start="1189" data-end="1220" data-section-id="f475aq">
<p data-start="1192" data-end="1220">Go to <strong data-start="1198" data-end="1220"><a data-start="1200" data-end="1218" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/">https://github.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2df4e570.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1221" data-end="1249" data-section-id="37u2h3">
<p data-start="1224" data-end="1249">Click <strong data-start="1230" data-end="1248">New Repository</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1250" data-end="1274" data-section-id="mn3pc7">
<p data-start="1253" data-end="1274">Name it, for example:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1276" data-end="1294"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2df4e570.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>ArtGallery</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="4" data-start="1296" data-end="1382">
<li data-start="1296" data-end="1327" data-section-id="iqwqih">
<p data-start="1299" data-end="1327">Click <strong data-start="1305" data-end="1326">Create Repository</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1329" data-end="1370" data-section-id="mj5db1">
<p data-start="1332" data-end="1370">Click <strong data-start="1338" data-end="1350">Add file</strong> → <strong data-start="1353" data-end="1369">Upload files</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1372" data-end="1382" data-section-id="hvmcjo">
<p data-start="1375" data-end="1382">Upload:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start="1383" data-end="1423">
<li data-start="1383" data-end="1399" data-section-id="1rxnltt">
<p data-start="1385" data-end="1399">All HTML files</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1400" data-end="1423" data-section-id="v3b73n">
<p data-start="1402" data-end="1423">The <strong data-start="1406" data-end="1416">images</strong> folder</p>
</li>
</ul>
<ol start="7" data-start="1425" data-end="1453">
<li data-start="1425" data-end="1453" data-section-id="yb0mzc">
<p data-start="1428" data-end="1453">Click <strong data-start="1434" data-end="1452">Commit changes</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1455" data-end="1458">
<h2 data-start="1460" data-end="1485" data-section-id="1pk6tx6">5. Enable GitHub Pages</h2>
<ol data-start="1487" data-end="1690">
<li data-start="1487" data-end="1511" data-section-id="im496b">
<p data-start="1490" data-end="1511">Open your repository.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1512" data-end="1534" data-section-id="s9n6t8">
<p data-start="1515" data-end="1534">Click <strong data-start="1521" data-end="1533">Settings</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1535" data-end="1554" data-section-id="sck8s8">
<p data-start="1538" data-end="1554">Click <strong data-start="1544" data-end="1553">Pages</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1555" data-end="1613" data-section-id="1212dbv">
<p data-start="1558" data-end="1583">Under <strong data-start="1564" data-end="1574">Source</strong>, select:</p>
<ul data-start="1587" data-end="1613">
<li data-start="1587" data-end="1613" data-section-id="1o2dv8g">
<p data-start="1589" data-end="1613"><strong data-start="1589" data-end="1613">Deploy from a branch</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1614" data-end="1671" data-section-id="1nbm6tp">
<p data-start="1617" data-end="1624">Select:</p>
<ul data-start="1628" data-end="1671">
<li data-start="1628" data-end="1646" data-section-id="yhyb2l">
<p data-start="1630" data-end="1646">Branch: <strong data-start="1638" data-end="1646">main</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1650" data-end="1671" data-section-id="x5ol4c">
<p data-start="1652" data-end="1671">Folder: <strong data-start="1660" data-end="1671">/(root)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1672" data-end="1690" data-section-id="ibgw8s">
<p data-start="1675" data-end="1690">Click <strong data-start="1681" data-end="1689">Save</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1692" data-end="1750">After 1–5 minutes, GitHub will generate your website link.</p>
<p data-start="1752" data-end="1770">It will look like:</p>
