s completion. Use it to generate a new completion. The output should be a standalone response that reflects the feedback without acknowledging it. Do not mention, suggest, or imply that this is a revision, improvement, or result of feedback. Respond in the same language as the original completion, even if the feedback is in another language. Only switch if the feedback explicitly asks you to translate the completion. Here is the feedback:\\n\"},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"193245580\":{\"name\":\"193245580\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"windsurf\":\"windsurf:extension/openai.chatgpt\",\"vscodeExtensionAppId\":\"openai.chatgpt\",\"vscode\":\"vscode:extension/openai.chatgpt\",\"cursor\":\"cursor:extension/openai.chatgpt\",\"cli\":\"https://developers.openai.com/codex/cli\",\"cursorExtensionAppId\":\"openai.chatgpt\",\"windsurfExtensionAppId\":\"openai.chatgpt\"},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"999809785\":{\"name\":\"999809785\",\"rule_id\":\"layerAssignment\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{},\"is_device_based\":false,\"is_experiment_active\":true,\"is_user_in_experiment\":false},\"3652260651\":{\"name\":\"3652260651\",\"rule_id\":\"3A7McZGS5T8bLSiH78K3Wa:100.00:10-3A7McY1PDAYHssKLw0OqD8\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"error_tone\":\"error-2025-11-19.wav\",\"thinking_tone\":\"thinking-2025-11-20.wav\",\"hangup_tone\":\"hangup_0db.ogg\"},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":true},\"2850107578\":{\"name\":\"2850107578\",\"rule_id\":\"5N0MtwWXXbm54tjHn0MqOn:100.00:1-5N0MtvhVuTcAL3LLLSQNvl\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"late_ads_event_discard_timeout_seconds\":5,\"android_large_font_scale_threshold\":1.5,\"ask_chatgpt_system_message\":\"The user is referring to an ad shown to them about: {LABEL}. Your response MUST BE ABOUT THE ADS shown, since the user explicitly asked about them. They are using the 'Ask ChatGPT' feature and you must reply to the user query using the information about the ads, which is:\\n{DATA}\\n\\nFor example: if the user asks 'Tell me more about these' (or other wordings), then your answer should be about details or further information on products, services, locations etc described in the ad and the links in the ad.\",\"android_display_zoom_scale_threshold\":1,\"late_ads_event_discard_timeout_after_message_end_visibility_seconds\":1,\"onboarding\":{\"screen_personalization_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/bazaar/onboarding/personalization_en.png\",\"impression_count\":5,\"card_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/onboarding/onboarding-example-1.png\",\"screen_transparency_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/bazaar/onboarding/controls_en.png\",\"screen_trust_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/bazaar/onboarding/trusted_en.png\",\"screen_privacy_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/bazaar/onboarding/secure.png\"}},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":true},\"3165814200\":{\"name\":\"3165814200\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"MIN_RETRY_INTERVAL\":300,\"RETRY_FACTOR\":1.5,\"MAX_RETRY_INTERVAL\":5000,\"MAX_RETRY_COUNT\":12,\"JITTER_MINIMUM\":0.5,\"JITTER_MAXIMUM\":1},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"1001765573\":{\"name\":\"1001765573\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[{\"gate\":\"4113286138\",\"gateValue\":\"false\",\"ruleID\":\"default\"},{\"gate\":\"1829150232\",\"gateValue\":\"false\",\"ruleID\":\"default\"}],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"3317473948\":{\"name\":\"3317473948\",\"rule_id\":\"2VVKrjIwc2VcBceUZhfkJB:100.00:3\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"default_max_polling_duration\":200,\"model_slug_max_polling_durations\":{\"o3_pro\":1200,\"o1_pro\":1200,\"image_gen\":300},\"d